keting 手法<br />\n你可以話冇講過係官方project 冇講過係game 冇乜乜柒柒<br />\n不過你地一開始個宣傳點解咁做自己心照啦"},{"pid":"70f8b52788587501447be1c5daccd8021c818089","tid":2403841,"uid":58391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:46:05.000Z","msg":"樓上咁大仇口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f728e6fa550f460c70feac4bcc26d6fe45de74","tid":2403841,"uid":20820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"邪鬼粒lin都係紫色"},{"pid":"af797a027e83a87744726a4e1bec11244d046bb7","tid":2403841,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac5d6946229fccb05e9a13b5f17d62d20404edea","tid":2403841,"uid":221435,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"出咗啦!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aBU3vFYea7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaBU3vFYea7U&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=86997456\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aBU3vFYea7U</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"好正 雖然回憶中啲畫質冇咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebe20295f0739da35f20c46bd3662ddfdd9bbc1","tid":2403841,"uid":131692,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70f8b52788587501447be1c5daccd8021c818089","tid":2403841,"uid":58391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:46:05.000Z","msg":"樓上咁大仇口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy